{"tid":244671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"花2100元買複式食白果　博士諗計最少有安慰獎","createTime":"2017-05-15T15:14:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T06:03:30.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"723750bc6163ed849259413510f68d02c640ae1a","tid":244671,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:14:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=W0AoVUN-iZA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DW0AoVUN-iZA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a1556575\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=W0AoVUN-iZA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n發佈日期：2017年5月15日相關連結:<br />\n【六合彩必中法】實測結果連中多獎 投注四千蚊只換1100獎金<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/3FsU4F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F3FsU4F&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=64ee0840\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/3FsU4F</a><br />\n<br />\n【六合彩必中法】專家教買六合彩貼士 秘技原來係<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/QzRYRM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FQzRYRM&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=e45d85ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/QzRYRM</a><br />\n_________________<br />\n《壹週刊》周一頭條 :<br />\n【生意●微賺萬五】90後掟百萬搞VR遊戲場 女士喪叫男士食花生<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/uzKCTy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FuzKCTy&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=5cf1352c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/uzKCTy</a><br />\n<br />\n《壹週刊》周一娛頭 :<br />\n【含劇透●接收Gordon舊菜】Mall姐阻不了 《不懂撒嬌的女人》劉丹于淼忘年戀奉子成婚<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/7fwDVK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2F7fwDVK&d=wSR7%2FpLLUFbraZn9MQiPfHIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=53abfa03\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/7fwDVK</a><br />\n<br />\n人人都想中六合彩，不講不知，原來在蘋果App Store，有一個叫「六合彩必中法」的App，只要支付八元就買到這個App，聲稱可以幫你「坐七獎（安慰獎）望頭獎」。<br />\n<br />\n中獎方法就是買其計算出來的399注組合，想知是否有效，就要看另一段實測報道。《壹》仔找到開發者William Lam，但他只肯透過電郵回覆。<br />\n<br />\n「當初因為未中過六合彩，安慰獎都未中過，曾經花2,100蚊買十個號碼嘅複式組合，最終一個號碼都唔中。自此有個念頭，究竟最少要買幾多注同點樣買，先可以確保一定中獎呢？就算中安慰獎，都叫做攞個尾彩。」William解釋設計這個App的原因。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，自己於香港大學電子工程系博士畢業，精於算術，大約五年前利用複雜的程式加上電腦協助，足足花了三個月才計算出這個必中法。「用咗自己個App之後，打破從未中獎嘅厄運，中過四獎、五獎、六獎同安慰獎。」<br />\n<br />\nWilliam 都未中過頭獎，四獎其實只是固定派彩9,600元。他又強調，399注是他暫時計算到最少必中安慰獎的組合，可以減少每注與每注之間不必要的重複號碼，從而增加中獎機會同金額。<br />\n<br />\n這個App的免費版，只提供必中兩個號碼及必中一個號碼，分別要買43注和8注，你要支付8元，才能得知必中安慰獎方法。William強調不是打算要賺什麼錢，買App的人亦不多，亦沒統計過有幾多人買，只是免費版有少量廣告收入。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：李啟發<br />\n攝影：莫智謙、傅俊偉"},{"pid":"5e6095a64c3e4d12b3467db2aaf842e81561fd91","tid":244671,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T15:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9a7b3bceff7fa17c281b13aca861bb6c3c83962","tid":244671,"uid":7840,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T16:02:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6a48dddbc7a0859f58765c2ec033aec6899b9322","tid":244671,"uid":49197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T19:45:58.000Z","msg":"六合彩根本冇得度，賭馬同波好過啦"},{"pid":"c1efa1ee9f939890aa616eac075d5f4dbe79dd5a","tid":244671,"uid":9394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:05:18.000Z","msg":"On99 讀過中學統計prob都識計啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e4e2c5b0d019c91f850b9229e9399562b34665e","tid":244671,"uid":28588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:13:18.000Z","msg":"你要支付8元，才能得知必中安慰獎方法<br />\n<br />\n姐係點？跟佢買哂咁多注 先中一注？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5958cc1a42f147bd5350a84a69b60d45a2673987","tid":244671,"uid":16956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T20:16:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"817b2ed7de60ae9d8f66c736e24c64adbe7797f7","tid":244671,"uid":61130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:38:17.000Z","msg":"安慰獎會唔會一齊分<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3606e7085ddb8b98bc468cf6a2001f1431a0e1d","tid":244671,"uid":10571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:39:31.000Z","msg":"賭波必勝法<br />\n主客和各一注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe279364a1a84c035413403da715ffbbf292ea6","tid":244671,"uid":75193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-15T22:44:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賭波必勝法<br />\n主客和各一注<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁不如買入波/角球大細 買少樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54297e574902784dad32d961cce969f874638608","tid":244671,"uid":34223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T06:03:30.000Z","msg":"又係時候用詹培忠賭波必勝法啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}